Cyber Claw:




Cyber Claw paused and watched Serpentor and Koga by the tree. She changed 
her mind, Serpentor would have to do. He was damaged, so that meant that he 
would be less of a fight. She charged back at him, baring her jagged teeth 
as she flew at the two. She screamed and throwing her foot out just in case 
Koga decided to protect him. She grabbed  Serpentor by the back armor, 
holding to him tight. She lifted him up and headed for the forest.

"You and I are going to have a talk about Megatron!" she said to him. She 
then lowered her head to him and shouted shrilly. "And I am not an Autobot! 
I am a Predacon!"
